[FRIEND 7A]
Gotcha.

00:10:32.257 --> 00:10:33.049 position:50% align:center
[FRIEND 7B]
C'mon. Let's go.

00:10:33.133 --> 00:10:34.175 position:50% align:center
Are you sure?

00:10:34.259 --> 00:10:36.428 position:50% align:center
Yeah. Right now,
the only mission I have

00:10:36.511 --> 00:10:38.722 position:50% align:center
is to recruit you
as my personal model!

00:10:38.805 --> 00:10:40.098 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO]
Sorry, I've gotta pass.

00:10:40.181 --> 00:10:43.101 position:50% align:center
Aww. That's twice
in a row now, bummer.

00:10:43.184 --> 00:10:44.144 position:50% align:center
Twice in a row?

00:10:44.227 --> 00:10:47.188 position:50% align:center
Yeah. Remember
in middle school?

00:10:47.272 --> 00:10:49.024 position:50% align:center
I wanted you to model
in girl clothes.

00:10:49.107 --> 00:10:51.359 position:50% align:center
But you shot me down then, too.

00:10:53.028 --> 00:10:54.404 position:50% align:center
You'd look cute!

00:10:54.487 --> 00:10:56.239 position:50% align:center
Forget it.

00:10:56.322 --> 00:10:58.199 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO] Hold on,
that was what you meant?

00:10:58.283 --> 00:11:00.910 position:50% align:center
Huh? What was what I meant?

00:11:02.037 --> 00:11:03.246 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO] I always figured
that she wanted

00:11:03.329 --> 00:11:04.956 position:50% align:center
to take photos of me
in girls' clothes

00:11:05.040 --> 00:11:07.417 position:50% align:center
so she could make fun
of me or something.

00:11:07.500 --> 00:11:10.337 position:50% align:center
[MAKIMURA] Here's the thing.
When we were in middle school,

00:11:10.420 --> 00:11:12.213 position:50% align:center
your features were
soft and elegant!

00:11:12.297 --> 00:11:13.965 position:50% align:center
Dare I say androgynous?

00:11:14.049 --> 00:11:17.177 position:50% align:center
Anyway, as soon as I noticed
that, I knew I had to paint you!

00:11:17.260 --> 00:11:19.387 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO]
I completely misread her.

00:11:20.263 --> 00:11:21.723 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO]
What's up?

00:11:21.806 --> 00:11:23.516 position:50% align:center
Trying to decide what kind of
outfits you'd look best in,

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:25.226 position:50% align:center
since your frame's
a bit more masculine now.

00:11:25.310 --> 00:11:27.187 position:50% align:center
