from a romance drama.

00:19:39.179 --> 00:19:40.472 position:50% align:center
It's pretty recent.

00:19:40.555 --> 00:19:42.891 position:50% align:center
Oh, right. I remember now.

00:19:42.974 --> 00:19:45.393 position:50% align:center
