00:19:52.317 --> 00:19:54.194 position:50% align:center
The mood is totally different
from the second track on.

00:19:54.277 --> 00:19:56.237 position:50% align:center
I think you'd really like it.

00:19:56.321 --> 00:19:59.240 position:50% align:center
Oh, well, in that case,
I'd love to try it.

00:19:59.324 --> 00:20:01.951 position:50% align:center
Sure. I'll bring it
with me tomorrow then.

00:20:02.035 --> 00:20:04.954 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO] I guess lending people
CDs is pretty common.

00:20:05.038 --> 00:20:07.165 position:50% align:center
I've never been one to do that.

00:20:07.248 --> 00:20:08.792 position:50% align:center
[SASAKI]
Well, I do it all the time.

00:20:08.875 --> 00:20:11.544 position:50% align:center
Ogasawara likes a lot of
the same bands I do.

00:20:11.628 --> 00:20:13.922 position:50% align:center
Oh, here,
I pulled up the lyrics.

00:20:14.005 --> 00:20:15.298 position:50% align:center
Borrowing CDs is cool 'cause

00:20:15.382 --> 00:20:17.759 position:50% align:center
