00:20:22.055 --> 00:20:23.932 position:50% align:center
I like holding the
physical copy in my hand,

00:20:24.015 --> 00:20:25.433 position:50% align:center
it's a whole lot better!

00:20:25.517 --> 00:20:26.559 position:50% align:center
[SASAKI]
I like him.

